Package medical

package medical
This package contains medical-related classes for the insurance system. It includes classes for medical records, healthcare providers, and visit types.

The classes in this package help manage medical data linked to patients.

  • Class
    Description
    DiagnosticCode
    Represents a diagnostic code based on the ICD-10 classification.
    HealthcareProvider
    Represents a healthcare provider such as a hospital or clinic.
    MedicalRecord
    Represents a patient's medical record in the insurance system.
    Medication
    Represents a medication with associated details loaded from a CSV file.
    ProcedureCode
    Represents a medical procedure code with associated description, category, and price.
    TypeOfVisit
    Defines the type of visit (Inpatient, Outpatient) for a patient.
